column2: THIS IS BRAVO BLACK. WE THOUGHT TO GIVE YOU GUYS A HAND. HOWS IT GOING DOWN HERE. BRAVO OUT.
ALPHA BLACK TO PAPABEAR. ALL RUSSIAN FORCES HAVE BEEN DEFEATED. MEAUX UNDER CONTROL. OVER.
THIS IS PAPABEAR. THE RUSSIAN FORCES ARE ATTACKING FROM THE SOUTH. TAKE DEFENSIVE POSITIONS AND REPEL THE BASTARDS. OVER.
